                </div>

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>

      <!-- Energy Panel -->
      <div class="tab-panel" id="panel-energy">
        <div class="grid-3" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <div class="card stat-card">
            <span class="stat-label">Programs Since 2021</span>
            <span class="stat-value">7</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card stat-card">
            <span class="stat-label">Capital Deployed</span>
            <span class="stat-value">$6.2M+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card stat-card">
            <span class="stat-label">Wells Drilled</span>
            <span class="stat-value">30+</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="re-deal-description" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <p>Direct working interests in oil and gas drilling programs. Investors receive monthly distributions from well production and significant first-year tax deductions through intangible drilling costs (IDC).</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">Early investments provided valuable operational learning. As a result, we have shifted toward partnering with larger operators with stronger balance sheets, repeatable drilling programs, and proven production histories.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bidwell Capital Upstream Energy Fund -->
        <article class="re-deal-card">
          <div class="re-deal-header">
            <div>
              <h3>Bidwell Capital Upstream Energy Fund</h3>
              <span class="re-deal-location">Powder River Basin &mdash; 2025</span>
            </div>
            <span class="re-deal-status re-deal-active">Active / Deploying</span>
          </div>
          <div class="re-deal-body">
            <div class="re-deal-stats">
              <div class="re-deal-stat">
                <span class="re-deal-stat-label">Investment</span>
                <span class="re-deal-stat-value">$525,000</span>
              </div>
              <div class="re-deal-stat">
                <span class="re-deal-stat-label">Underlying Fund</span>
                <span class="re-deal-stat-value">Aspen Upstream Energy Fund VII</span>
              </div>
              <div class="re-deal-stat">
                <span class="re-deal-stat-label">GP / Operator</span>
                <span class="re-deal-stat-value">Aspen Funds / Mahajer Energy</span>
              </div>
              <div class="re-deal-stat">
                <span class="re-deal-stat-label">Structure</span>
                <span class="re-deal-stat-value">Fund-of-Funds</span>
              </div>
              <div class="re-deal-stat">
                <span class="re-deal-stat-label">Basin</span>
                <span class="re-deal-stat-value">Powder River Basin (WY/MT)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="re-deal-stat">
                <span class="re-deal-stat-label">Status</span>
                <span class="re-deal-stat-value">Producing / Deploying</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="re-deal-description">
              <p>Bidwell Capital invested $525,000 as a fund-of-funds participant into Aspen Funds' Upstream Energy Fund VII. The strategy focuses on acquiring producing oil and gas wells (PDP assets) and reinvesting cash flow into new drilling opportunities to increase production and long-term returns. The fund is primarily targeting assets in the Powder River Basin and aims to purchase producing wells at discounted present value multiples.</p>
              <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">The fund provides indirect exposure to multiple assets including 92 producing wells in an initial acquisition, 2 Devon-operated wells already drilled and producing, and additional wells through future acquisitions and drilling programs. Underlying operators include Devon Energy, EOG Resources, Continental Resources, and other Powder River Basin operators.</p>
              <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">Early drilling investments in Devon-operated offset wells have begun producing and are performing in line with expectations. The fund also includes exposure to proven undeveloped drilling locations that may be developed over time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Oil Fund VI -->
        <article class="re-deal-card" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <div class="re-deal-header">
            <div>
              <h3>Oil Fund VI - Rush Creek</h3>
              <span class="re-deal-location">2025</span>
            </div>
            <span class="re-deal-status re-deal-active">Producing</span>
          </div>
          <div class="re-deal-body">
            <div class="re-deal-stats">
              <div class="re-deal-stat">
                <span class="re-deal-stat-label">Capital Raised</span>
                <span class="re-deal-stat-value">$1,765,000</span>
              </div>
              <div class="re-deal-stat">
                <span class="re-deal-stat-label">Wells</span>
                <span class="re-deal-stat-value">11</span>
              </div>
              <div class="re-deal-stat">
                <span class="re-deal-stat-label">Production</span>
                <span class="re-deal-stat-value">~30 bbl/day/well</span>
              </div>
              <div class="re-deal-stat">
                <span class="re-deal-stat-label">Status</span>
                <span class="re-deal-stat-value">At pro forma</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="re-deal-description">
              <p>Most recent program reflecting our refined operator selection process. Eleven wells with Rush Creek Resources, currently producing at approximately pro forma levels.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Oil Fund V -->
        <article class="re-deal-card" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <div class="re-deal-header">
            <div>
              <h3>Oil Fund V - DW Energy / Fulcrum</h3>
              <span class="re-deal-location">2024</span>
            </div>
            <span class="re-deal-status re-deal-active">Producing</span>
          </div>
          <div class="re-deal-body">
            <div class="re-deal-stats">
              <div class="re-deal-stat">
